              (  1, 1, 2, 'VSLive! Las Vegas', 'vslive-las-vegas-2023', 'https://vslive.com/events/las-vegas-2023/home.aspx', 'Planet Hollywood Resort & Casino<br />Las Vegas, NV', 'Las Vegas, NV', '2023-03-19', '2023-03-24', '$650', '$3,600', 'Expert solutions for enterprise developers.', '<p>VSLive! Developer Conference has been training developers, software architects, engineers, and designers like you since 1993. As we celebrate our 30th Anniversary, we hope you will join us in Las Vegas, NV for six days of unbiased and cutting-edge education on the .NET Microsoft Platform. Sharpen your skills in Microsoft Visual Studio 2022, .NET 6, DevOps, MAUI, JavaScript, TypeScript, Angular, Blazor, modern data warehouse technology. Overall, our speakers will answer your questions with practical guidance on native client development, Web, database, and so much more.</p>'),
              (  2, 1, 2, 'InflectraCON', 'inflectracon-2023', 'https://www.inflectracon.com/home-2023', 'Kellogg Conference Center<br />Gallaudet University<br />Washington, DC', 'Washington, DC', '2023-04-19', '2023-04-21', '$534.69', '$899.99', 'Multi-track, multi-day conference that fosters enthusiasm for our software.', '<p>InflectraCON™ 2023 is a three-day multi-track conference celebrating all things Software Development, Testing, Agile, DevOps, Cyber, Leadership, and Innovation. Set in the heart of the nation’s capital, InflectraCON 2023 will have multiple conference tracks Quality, Agility, and Security. Be part of the most exhilarating conversations about digital transformation.</p><p>The conference will also host Inflectra’s Partner Summit and User Tutorials featuring user training, deep-dives, and certification on our award-winning platforms: Spira* and Rapise.</p><p>The event will be hosted in person in Washington, DC, on April 19-21, 2023!</p>'),
              (  3, 1, 2, 'Serverless Architecture Conference', 'serverless-architecture-conference-london-2023', 'https://serverless-architecture.io/london/', 'Park Plaza Victoria London', 'London', '2023-04-24', '2023-04-27', '£449', '£1599', 'Mastering Cloud Native Architectures, the Kubernetes Ecosystem and Functions', '<p><strong>INNOVATE FASTER</strong><br />From serverless platforms to functions: Modern cloud native technologies are pushing productivity to the next level.</p><p><strong>FOCUS ON WHAT REALLY MATTERS</strong><br />To take full advantage of this new dawn of deploying, scaling and managing applications software architects and developers need to re-focus the way they design software systems.<br /><strong>BUILD GREAT APPLICATIONS</strong><br />Join Serverless Architecture Conference and gain key knowledge and skills for this new era of computing. Being a software engineer has never been better.</p>'),
              (108, 3, 2, 'Orlando Code Camp', 'orlando-code-camp-2023', 'https://orlandocodecamp.com/', 'Seminole State College<br />Sanford, FL', 'Sanford, FL', '2023-03-25', '2023-03-25', 'Free', 'Free', 'Orlando Codecamp 2023 is organized by Orlando .NET User Group (ONETUG) and hosted by Seminole State College.', '<p>Orlando Codecamp 2023 is organized by Orlando .NET User Group (ONETUG) and hosted by Seminole State College. The event entry is <strong>FREE</strong> to all attendees, thanks to our generous sponsors. We will feature multiple tracks of hard core technical and tech industry-adjacent talks of 50 minutes each.</p>'),
              (109, 1, 2, 'DeveloperWeek Management 2023', 'developerweek-management-2023', 'https://www.developerweek.com/global/conference/management/', 'Virtual', 'Virtual', '2023-05-09', '2023-05-10', '$530', '$1555', 'The world''s largest developer & engineering conference & expo. Uniting the global developer community.', '<p>DeveloperWeek Management is the premier virtual conference & expo for engineering managers, dev team leads, and technical executives (VP, Director, CTO, CXO). Join 2,000+ virtual attendees for a fully immersive education and innovation experience, where you can learn & gain insights from top engineering leaders about team management, best practices, and developer tools & technology decision-making.</p><p>With a fully immersive virtual experience, we’re bringing you: 6+ tracks, 40+ speakers, 7 technical keynotes, a live 2-day Virtual Expo with 15+ technologies & tools, product demos, and 1:1 topic-focused networking.</p><p>Speakers include leaders from IBM, VMware, AWS, Stack Overflow, Wix.com, Lucid Software, Turing, New York Times, LinearB, Foursquare, MariaDB, and many more.)</p>'),
              (110, 1, 2, 'Prairie Dev Con', 'prairie-dev-con-winnipeg-2023a', 'https://www.prairiedevcon.com/winnipeg.html', 'Canad Inns Destination Centre Polo Park<br />Winnipeg, MB', 'Winnipeg, MB', '2023-06-12', '2023-06-13', 'C$725', 'C$825', 'Bringing a software conference experience to the Canadian prairies', '<p>Prairie Dev Con started in 2010 with the goal of bringing a software conference experience to the Canadian prairies! 12 years later and we''re excited to be bringing the conference back to Winnipeg in 2022!</p>'),
              (111, 1, 6, 'KCDC', 'kcdc-2023', 'https://www.kcdc.info/', 'Kansas City Convention Center<br />Kansas City, MO', 'Kansas City, MO', '2023-06-21', '2023-06-23', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Kansas City''s premier educational conference for software development.', '<p>The Kansas City Developer Conference is excited to announce our 14th annual event! Our 2023 conference will be held June 21-23, 2023, with a pre-conference workshop day and two full conference days. Once again, the event will be held at the Kansas City Convention Center in downtown Kansas City. Each year, we draw a large audience of new and experienced Developers, Architects, UI/UX Designers, QA Professionals, PMs, and Technology Managers from Missouri, Kansas, Illinois, Nebraska, Iowa, Minnesota, Oklahoma, the Dakotas, and around the United States and the world. We hope you will join us!</p>'),
              (112, 1, 2, 'Scenic City Summit', 'scenic-city-summit-2023a', 'https://sceniccitysummit.com/', 'Chattanooga Convention Center<br />Chattanooga, TN', 'Chattanooga, TN', '2023-06-02', '2023-06-02', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Scenic City Summit is a one-day technology conference based in Chattanooga, TN.', '<p>Chattanooga’s largest local IT professional development conference. Connecting professionals across industries, platforms, & businesses to share new methodologies, emerging technologies, & practical knowledge on unique, engaging topics.</p><p>Scenic City Summit started in 2016 as a community developer conference held at the Engineering, Math, and Computer Science building.  Since then it has moved to the Chattanooga Convention Center and expanded the content to include data science, cloud & DevOps, UX/UI, and other topics to make SCS an event for technical professionals throughout the region.</p>'),
              (113, 2, 2, 'Louisville .NET Meetup', 'loudotnet-february-2023', 'https://www.meetup.com/louisville-dotnet/events/291459813/', 'Modis<br />Louisville, KY', 'Louisville, KY', '2023-02-16', '2023-02-16', 'Free', 'Free', 'The Louisville .NET Meetup group is dedicated to helping developers around Louisville to become better developers.', '<p>The Louisville .NET Meetup group is dedicated to helping developers around Louisville to become better developers with an emphasis on the Microsoft .NET technology stack. We hold meetings on the third Thursday of each month.</p>'),
              (114, 1, 2, 'Agile & Beyond', 'agile-and-beyond-2023', 'http://www.agileandbeyond.com/2023/', 'Huntington Place<br />Detroit, MI', 'Detroit, MI', '2023-06-13', '2023-06-14', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'The premier annual Agile software development conference in the Great Lakes region', '<p>From small beginnings to explosive growth, Agile & Beyond has always stayed true to our roots. We pride ourselves on selecting speakers and topics that appeal to a wide range of roles including product owners, managers, designers, developers and executives alike.</p><p>Drawing premier speakers and the highest caliber practitioners in the industry, this annual conference in Detroit, MI sells out every year attracting nearly 1,500 Agile enthusiasts and practitioners globally with top tier keynotes, fantastic sessions, and the industries leading companies exhibiting their latest innovations and job opportunities.</p>'),
              (115, 1, 2, 'Beer City Code', 'beer-city-code-2023', 'https://www.beercitycode.com/', 'Calvin University - Fine Arts Center<br />Grand Rapids, MI', 'Grand Rapids, MI', '2023-08-04', '2023-08-05', '$79', '$149', 'Annual Software Conference held in the amazing Beer City of Grand Rapids, MI', '<p>Beer City Code is an annual conference for software developers held in Grand Rapids, MI, also known as <a href="https://www.experiencegr.com/things-to-do/beer-city/" target="_top">Beer City, USA</a>. Software creators of all types are welcome, even those who don''t care for beer.</p><p>The main conference is held Saturday, August 6. Note that, as we return to our first event since COVID, we will be keeping the event simple this year. There will be no workshops, diversity mixer, kids conference, or keynote for the 2022 event. We hope that these features of the show will return in 2023.</p><p>The Beer City Code conference grew our of the success of its predecessor, Grand Rapids DevDay, but was renamed in 2017 to embrace its much more broad appeal outside the Grand Rapids area.</p>'),
