              (117, 1, 2, 'JavaScript & Friends', 'javascript-and-friends-2023', 'https://www.javascriptandfriends.com/', 'Quest Conference Center<br />Columbus, OH', 'Columbus, OH', '2023-08-25', '2023-08-25', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Javascript & Friends is JS based conference by software professionals for software professionals and for those aspiring to be one.', '<p>The JavaScript & Friends Conference is a not-for-profit conference and entirely volunteer run. We are a group of software and technology professionals seeking to bring together a diverse group of JavaScript enthusiasts and friends to learn and network. With this conference, we seek to contribute to the cultivation of a welcoming, inclusive and dynamic tech scene throughout Ohio and the midwestern United States.</p>'),
